 data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-pKreJ jowHiA pf-106_ pf-image-1" store="[object Object]"/><p class="sc-iowYbt eEPszQ pf-107_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-70cacd06-e395-41a8-a564-31dfb8aeb010"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Mit Edelstahlkugel</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-cd96" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bcSJDS dsCpLi pf-110_ pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-enkJyZ gKpywE"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-111_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-112_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cTTcKX ejfvWQ pf-113_ pf-heading-3-h3">FULL ROUTINE</h3><div data-pf-type="Slideshow" class="sc-iXzffn etgRQt pf-115_"><div data-id="slider-511ad9ca-cd13-46ab-8059-c15fdea198dc-all" class="pf-slider scrollfix" style="--ws-xs:60;--ss-xs:1;--ss-sm:2;--ss-md:3;--ss-lg:3"><div class="pf-slide"><div class="sc-bJUkdm fydhRR pf-116_" data-pf-type="SlideshowSlide"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-117_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:3;--c-md:4;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-118_"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 512" data-pf-type="Icon2" class="sc-lgjIEp eKorth pf-119_"><path d="M160 64c0-11.8-6.5-22.6-16.9-28.2s-23-5-32.8 1.6l-96 64C-.5 111.2-4.4 131 5.4 145.8s29.7 18.7 44.4 8.9L96 123.8V416H32c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32h96 96c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H160V64z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:9;--c-md:8;--c-lg:9"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-120_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cTTcKX ejfvWQ pf-121_">Reinigung</h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-123_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-124_"><p class="sc-iowYbt eEPszQ pf-125_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-84e957ae-1274-4a4d-99a6-b3c041214d5f"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Starte morgens und abends mit der Reinigung. Morgens reicht oft lauwarmes Wasser oder ein mildes Gel, um Schweiß und Talg zu entfernen. Abends gründlich reinigen, um Schmutz, SPF und überschüssiges Öl zu lösen – die Basis, damit alles danach besser wirkt.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-slide"><div class="sc-bJUkdm fydhRR pf-128_" data-pf-type="SlideshowSlide"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-129_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:3;--c-md:4;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-130_"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512" data-pf-type="Icon2" class="sc-lgjIEp eKorth pf-131_"><path d="M142.9 96c-21.5 0-42.2 8.5-57.4 23.8L54.6 150.6c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L40.2 74.5C67.5 47.3 104.4 32 142.9 32C223 32 288 97 288 177.1c0 38.5-15.3 75.4-42.5 102.6L109.3 416H288c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32s-14.3 32-32 32H32c-12.9 0-24.6-7.8-29.6-19.8s-2.2-25.7 6.9-34.9L200.2 234.5c15.2-15.2 23.8-35.9 23.8-57.4c0-44.8-36.3-81.1-81.1-81.1z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:9;--c-md:8;--c-lg:9"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-132_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cTTcKX ejfvWQ pf-133_">Toner / Gesichtswasser</h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-135_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-136_"><p class="sc-iowYbt eEPszQ pf-137_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-54ab515d-57ab-463f-aa5c-c8021200bcfc"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Trage ein alkoholfreies Gesichtswasser auf, um die Haut zu beruhigen, den pH-Wert auszubalancieren und Feuchtigkeit nachzulegen. Mit den Händen einklopfen, nicht reiben. Exfolierende Toner (AHA/BHA) nur abends und 2–3× pro Woche verwenden.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-slide"><div class="sc-bJUkdm fydhRR pf-140_" data-pf-type="SlideshowSlide"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-141_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:3;--c-md:4;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-142_"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512" data-pf-type="Icon2" class="sc-lgjIEp eKorth pf-143_"><path d="M0 64C0 46.3 14.3 32 32 32H272c13.2 0 25 8.1 29.8 20.4s1.5 26.3-8.2 35.2L162.3 208H184c75.1 0 136 60.9 136 136s-60.9 136-136 136H105.4C63 480 24.2 456 5.3 418.1l-1.9-3.8c-7.9-15.8-1.5-35 14.3-42.9s35-1.5 42.9 14.3l1.9 3.8c8.1 16.3 24.8 26.5 42.9 26.5H184c39.8 0 72-32.2 72-72s-32.2-72-72-72H80c-13.2 0-25-8.1-29.8-20.4s-1.5-26.3 8.2-35.2L189.7 96H32C14.3 96 0 81.7 0 64z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:9;--c-md:8;--c-lg:9"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-144_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cTTcKX ejfvWQ pf-145_">Serum</h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-147_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-148_"><p class="sc-iowYbt eEPszQ pf-149_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-82fd510a-36d3-432a-b917-1a1f7ae6f440"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Setze auf konzentrierte Wirkstoffe passend zu deinem Ziel: Hyaluron für Feuchtigkeit, Niacinamid für Poren und Glanz, Vitamin C am Morgen für Schutz und Strahlkraft, Retinol abends für glattere Haut. Erst wasserbasierte, dann öligere Seren. Kurz einziehen lassen.  </span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-slide"><div class="sc-bJUkdm fydhRR pf-152_" data-pf-type="SlideshowSlide"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-153_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-154_"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 384 512" data-pf-type="Icon2" class="sc-lgjIEp eKorth pf-155_"><path d="M189 77.6c7.5-16 .7-35.1-15.3-42.6s-35.1-.7-42.6 15.3L3 322.4c-4.7 9.9-3.9 21.5 1.9 30.8S21 368 32 368H256v80c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32V368h32c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H320V160c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32V304H82.4L189 77.6z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:8;--c-md:8;--c-lg:9"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-156_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cTTcKX ejfvWQ pf-157_">Augenpflege</h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-159_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-160_"><p class="sc-iowYbt eEPszQ pf-161_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-a9b9a98f-9f17-46cd-95d6-f910cc6a7905"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Eine kleine Menge unter dem Auge entlang des Jochbeins auftupfen oder mit dem Roll-On auftragen. Koffein hilft gegen Schwellungen, Peptide gegen feine Linien, Hyaluron gegen Trockenheit. Sanft einklopfen – nicht ziehen.   </span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-slide"><div class="sc-bJUkdm fydhRR pf-164_" data-pf-type="SlideshowSlide"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-165_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-166_"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512" data-pf-type="Icon2" class="sc-lgjIEp eKorth pf-167_"><path d="M32.5 58.3C35.3 43.1 48.5 32 64 32H256c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32s-14.3 32-32 32H90.7L70.3 208H184c75.1 0 136 60.9 136 136s-60.9 136-136 136H100.5c-39.4 0-75.4-22.3-93-57.5l-4.1-8.2c-7.9-15.8-1.5-35 14.3-42.9s35-1.5 42.9 14.3l4.1 8.2c6.8 13.6 20.6 22.1 35.8 22.1H184c39.8 0 72-32.2 72-72s-32.2-72-72-72H32c-9.5 0-18.5-4.2-24.6-11.5s-8.6-16.9-6.9-26.2l32-176z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:8;--c-md:8;--c-lg:9"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-168_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cTTcKX ejfvWQ pf-169_">Creme / Moisturizer </h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-171_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-172_"><p class="sc-iowYbt eEPszQ pf-173_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-1620ca49-f6d1-426f-b272-ff0e6914ec4b"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Fixiere die Feuchtigkeit und stärke die Barriere. Tagsüber eine leichte, schnell einziehende Textur; abends eine reichhaltigere Pflege, wenn die Haut mehr braucht. Gleichmäßig auf Gesicht und Hals verteilen.    </span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-slide"><div class="sc-bJUkdm fydhRR pf-176_" data-pf-type="SlideshowSlide"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-177_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-178_"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512" data-pf-type="Icon2" class="sc-lgjIEp eKorth pf-179_"><path d="M232.4 84.7c11.4-13.5 9.7-33.7-3.8-45.1s-33.7-9.7-45.1 3.8L38.6 214.7C14.7 242.9 1.1 278.4 .1 315.2c0 1.4-.1 2.9-.1 4.3c0 .2 0 .3 0 .5c0 88.4 71.6 160 160 160s160-71.6 160-160c0-85.5-67.1-155.4-151.5-159.8l63.9-75.6zM256 320A96 96 0 1 1 64 320a96 96 0 1 1 192 0z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:8;--c-md:8;--c-lg:9"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-180_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cTTcKX ejfvWQ pf-181_">Sonnenschutz (SPF)  </h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-183_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-184_"><p class="sc-iowYbt eEPszQ pf-185_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-a8473b28-75af-4dba-8b19-50cb60bb59fe"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Morgens als letzten Schritt: Breitband-SPF 30–50 großzügig auf Gesicht, Ohren und Hals auftragen. Bei längerer UV-Exposition alle zwei Stunden nachlegen. Ohne konsequenten SPF verliert jede Routine an Wirkung.     </span></p></div></div></div></div></div><button type="button" style="visibility:hidden" aria-label="Previous" class="pf-slider-prev nav-style-1 "></button><button type="button" style="visibility:hidden" aria-label="Next" class="pf-slider-next nav-style-1 "></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-250b" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bcSJDS dsCpLi pf-188_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-enkJyZ gKpywE"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-189_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-190_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cTTcKX ejfvWQ pf-191_ pf-heading-3-h3">DER FRISCHEKICK FÜR DEINE AUGENPARTIE</h3><img alt="vh-nh.png__PID:c0beab1a-9998-4fd1-bda2-3f5f2901e56a" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0317/7116/4804/files/vh-nh.png?v=175975941