{% endif %}</div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-f974" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bcSJDS dsCpLi pf-634_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:700px" class="sc-enkJyZ gKpywE"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-635_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:8px;--s-sm:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-636_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cTTcKX ejfvWQ pf-637_ pf-heading-7-h1">Du hast Fragen?</h3><div class="sc-gOqwAI jjtufm pf-639_ pf-icon-right" data-scroll-to-top="true" data-open-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3"><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-640_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-641_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="35a8bfde-3573-481e-b107-7b70198b9d1b" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Für wen ist der Augen Roll-On geeignet?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-643_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-644_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-645_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-646_"><p class="sc-lmUbDS cFVOqs pf-647_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Der Roll-On wurde speziell für Männerhaut entwickelt, die zu Schwellungen, Augenringen oder ersten Fältchen neigt. Er eignet sich für alle Hauttypen – auch empfindliche Haut.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-649_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-650_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="4ea094e1-57d1-4af1-bef2-9448de82b359" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Wie wirkt der Augen Roll-On gegen Augenringe und Schwellungen? </span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-652_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-653_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-654_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-655_"><p class="sc-lmUbDS cFVOqs pf-656_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Die Formel enthält Koffein, das die Mikrozirkulation anregt und so Schwellungen sowie dunkle Schatten mindert. Der kühlende Metall-Roll-On verstärkt den Sofort-Effekt.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-658_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-659_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="060deba1-11ae-4657-ab1b-15fdaf3c9e0f" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Hilft der Augen Roll-On auch gegen Falten?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-661_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-662_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-663_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-664_"><p class="sc-lmUbDS cFVOqs pf-665_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Ja. Der enthaltene Peptid-Komplex stärkt die Hautstruktur und beugt feinen Linien vor. In Kombination mit Hyaluronsäure, die intensiv Feuchtigkeit spendet, wirkt die Haut glatter und straffer. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-667_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-668_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="eb610e2e-4a60-466d-8413-99d27d74d253" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Wie oft sollte ich den Augen Roll-On anwenden?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-670_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-671_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-672_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-673_"><p class="sc-lmUbDS cFVOqs pf-674_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Für beste Ergebnisse morgens und abends nach der Gesichtsreinigung auftragen. Dank der handlichen Form kannst du ihn auch zwischendurch nutzen – ideal nach dem Sport oder bei Müdigkeit im Büro. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-676_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-677_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="52fe19de-1d51-43dc-87bf-e70079314f5f" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Kann ich den Augen Roll-On mit anderen Pflegeprodukten kombinieren?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-679_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-680_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-681_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-682_"><p class="sc-lmUbDS cFVOqs pf-683_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Ja. Der Roll-On ist als Teil deiner Pflegeroutine konzipiert: Nach Reinigung und Serum, vor deiner Gesichtscreme oder deinem Moisturizer. So entfaltet er die optimale Wirkung. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-685_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-686_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="14881ce1-460c-40d6-ac1c-c62572489c33" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Wie lange dauert es, bis ich Ergebnisse sehe?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-688_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-689_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-690_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-691_"><p class="sc-lmUbDS cFVOqs pf-692_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Der kühlende Effekt ist sofort spürbar. Erste Verbesserungen bei Schwellungen und Trockenheitsfältchen zeigen sich nach wenigen Anwendungen. Eine regelmäßige Nutzung über mehrere Wochen verstärkt den Effekt. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-694_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-695_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="c4a43b0a-d07a-41d3-80af-9f0628ff5ae1" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Ist der Augen Roll-On nur für Männer geeignet?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-697_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-698_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-699_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-700_"><p class="sc-lmUbDS cFVOqs pf-701_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Er wurde für die Bedürfnisse von Männerhaut entwickelt – kompakter, fettiger, dicker als Frauenhaut. Aber auch Frauen können ihn problemlos nutzen. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-703_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-704_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="d20a7321-3e25-4a87-b069-0b1517b2e5c5" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Ist der Augen Roll-On dermatologisch getestet?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-706_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-707_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-708_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-709_"><p class="sc-lmUbDS cFVOqs pf-710_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"> Ja, das Produkt ist dermatologisch getestet, Made in Germany und konform mit der EU-Kosmetikverordnung. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-9696" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-bcSJDS dsCpLi pf-712_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-enkJyZ gKpywE"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-713_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-dOorzJ liFmcT pf-714_"><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-bWJTsT bqQLUR pf-715_"><script src="https://widget.reviews.io/polaris/build.js"></script>
